==Test Vectors==

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Stack Value !! nSequence !! nVersion !! Result
|-
| 100 || 100 || 2 || Valid
|-
| 100 || 99 || 2 || Invalid (sequence too low)
|-
| 100 || 100 || 1 || Invalid (version < 2)
|-
| 0x80000000 || any || 2 || Valid (disabled in script)
|-
| 100 || 0x80000064 || 2 || Invalid (disabled in input)
|-
| 0x00400064 || 0x00000064 || 2 || Invalid (type mismatch)
|}

